{"tid":2261601,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件小學見過/做過嘅仆街事","createTime":"2020-10-28T12:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T17:29:47.000Z","uid":300420,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"38b83cc807d3aff673a87cc0ce829dc00df0ce8e","tid":2261601,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"話說我讀小四小五嘅時候同隔離班係坐喺一間四樓嘅班房一齊食飯嘅<br />\n當時另一班有個好樣衰嘅毒撚 所有人都排斥佢<br />\n<br />\n有一日我嗰班有個戇鳩仔剪咗個柒頭返嚟 不過佢平時都好撚燥底 所以冇人夠薑笑佢<br />\n<br />\n咁去到中午我哋都係咁樣照常食飯 食完飯之後冇嘢做就吹吓水啦 <br />\n<br />\n結果條毒撚走去恥笑條戇鳩仔 跟住俾人一下飛腳伸落春袋<br />\n<br />\n之後毒撚當場賴咗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊瀨屎一邊捉住春袋跑去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所到之處都有一條啡色嘅屎蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n四樓之後臭咗成個下晝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：當時見住成件事發生 笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但大個咗就知道成件事有幾醜惡（班教畜冇搞到條戇鳩仔之外 仲鬧條毒撚做乜瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"349f44ec6336aae3379847b075495ddb301d1653","tid":2261601,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd16a3f28118351acfba008b3abfd5fbaa32485","tid":2261601,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"樓主係瀨屎師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16634b13b0ec203b58ca2ace28792e377fd09a8c","tid":2261601,"uid":59795,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"會唔會成世陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879208aedfceb05958389ae74125148c399f7815","tid":2261601,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd16a3f28118351acfba008b3abfd5fbaa32485","tid":2261601,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"樓主係瀨屎師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"睇人瀨屎師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb1edea1eecf0f78c414c79526c9aff6965b9a1","tid":2261601,"uid":300420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16634b13b0ec203b58ca2ace28792e377fd09a8c","tid":2261601,"uid":59795,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"會唔會成世陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我幾年之後喺中學俾人拉咗返去一間教會 喺嗰度撞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢入咗一間唔係幾好嘅中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇乜朋友 似乎巳經唔想讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實嗰間教會我小學啲人都有返 可以睇得出嗰邊啲人其實都唔想佢留喺度 不過我都費事講到明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後覺得班人真係好仆街就走咗 唔知佢而家過成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7822979cb9849e081647bf2963ff5ea0e8e4a1bb","tid":2261601,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcb1edea1eecf0f78c414c79526c9aff6965b9a1","tid":2261601,"uid":300420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16634b13b0ec203b58ca2ace28792e377fd09a8c","tid":2261601,"uid":59795,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"會唔會成世陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我幾年之後喺中學俾人拉咗返去一間教會 喺嗰度撞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢入咗一間唔係幾好嘅中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇乜朋友 似乎巳經唔想讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實嗰間教會我小學啲人都有返 可以睇得出嗰邊啲人其實都唔想佢留喺度 不過我都費事講到明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後覺得班人真係好仆街就走咗 唔知佢而家過成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0G4qBg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0G4qBg.jpg&h=5721e0d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"478ea2c7b74aa1a0b6142241bc2ccc3f17fbf68e","tid":2261601,"uid":57255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"可能佢小學既時候大家俾多d接納認同佢，大個就唔會搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然老師都有佢責任既"},{"pid":"afe311c7f763a17eb25a4a0a5c720cc7f4f6e46d","tid":2261601,"uid":300420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"478ea2c7b74aa1a0b6142241bc2ccc3f17fbf68e","tid":2261601,"uid":57255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"可能佢小學既時候大家俾多d接納認同佢，大個就唔會搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然老師都有佢責任既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"佢嗰陣時好似匿埋左係個廁所到成個下晝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣時啲老師出去買條褲佢頂住先都好呀 冇不特止仲要怪人瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e423f854a58dc87adc55d47bebedc10ed1130944","tid":2261601,"uid":57255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"應該追究個肥仔，製造契機鼓勵大家接納佢呀...不過舊時d老師應該覺得唔好煩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家d老師可能好d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c5c12c609fa04e54bec6c01586155ca905644e","tid":2261601,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e423f854a58dc87adc55d47bebedc10ed1130944","tid":2261601,"uid":57255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"應該追究個肥仔，製造契機鼓勵大家接納佢呀...不過舊時d老師應該覺得唔好煩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家d老師可能好d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:50:48.000Z","msg":"兩個都係瘦撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係肥仔先會打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faea80061a2a248ad63996f481c03dcbbe277865","tid":2261601,"uid":309553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"點解個毒撚咁夠薑笑個戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca371703dd8f76f6b08e00cf3896d632a9b3e6a5","tid":2261601,"uid":273157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"燒著左肥閪老師條蕾絲裙<br />\n用肥閪老師內聯網帳號打辭職信比校長"},{"pid":"3ee6192360e1377ac7e2dbc38b4aacd44303045e","tid":2261601,"uid":300420,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"faea80061a2a248ad63996f481c03dcbbe277865","tid":2261601,"uid":309553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"點解個毒撚咁夠薑笑個戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"係佢最後嘅自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab12bebf7791dcce59dbe4f11637beeec0054184","tid":2261601,"uid":132810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"中一，<br />\n<br />\n有個因操行RETAKE咗兩年嘅女仔，<br />\n<br />\n成日冇端端超大聲鬧人，嚇到好多人彈起。仲要係哮你唔覺意，嚮正你身邊大叫。<br />\n<br />\n老師話極佢都喺咁。<br />\n<br />\n終於有次，班主任呀SIR竟然話